data.description: Great home in desirable Sherwood Forest! Come take a look at this charming 2 bedroom, 1 & 1/2 bathroom home nestled on a 0.34 acre lot. The property has a bonus room that is being used as a second master bedroom. Separate Laundry room. The house has a large shed in the fenced private back yard. Seller just replaced all windows, got a septic tank inspection, Hvac is 5 years old and was just serviced. The bedrooms are a nice size and the master suite has a walk in closets. This well-maintained property offers comfortable living space with an spacious living and dining area, which is perfect for entertaining. The fenced backyard is great for pets or the kids to run and play with ample outdoor space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home!
